{"tid":1010372,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Apex Legends》受歡迎 8小時玩家突破百萬","createTime":"2019-02-06T03:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T05:07:03.000Z","uid":66923,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad0e9d9ff0e6d770d2191fe1636931c3c6e70ec","tid":1010372,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"《泰坦降臨》開發商Respawn的免費大逃殺新作《Apex Legends》取得了一個不錯的開局，Respawn的CEO Vince Zampella在Twitter宣佈僅8小時，《Apex Legends》的玩家便突破了100萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6DKVVN8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DKVVN8.png&h=238b2a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我現在真是太驚喜了，《Apex Legends》8小時內就突破了100萬名玩家，非常感謝大家來玩，你們太棒了！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6aBFeW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6aBFeW.jpg&h=2be50b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Apex Legends》雖然看起來像借鑒了《鬥陣特攻》和《要塞英雄》，但它給人有一種基於《泰坦降臨》機制的獨特感受。<br />\n<br />\n目前《Apex Legends》已經登錄PS4，Xbox One和PC（Origin平臺）。"},{"pid":"addd4114f8c021c130cfbf505e442b1528f6f324","tid":1010372,"uid":18615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"隻game 既音效好正<br />\n用散彈時我個sub 仔比佢炸爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c206a60cfd694a33f0156c4a52ed119eaf8e329","tid":1010372,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20656312d5128a2da172769eaaa94a1ebcebaf36","tid":1010372,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7b617d20ae398602b4dbe3fde5aac9af736027","tid":1010372,"uid":3668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:50:31.000Z","msg":"的確幾好feel"},{"pid":"5ae8ed73ac